    "content": "# 成就&排行榜 v0.8\n\n成就&排行榜 v0.8 is the built-in guide for the `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard` Scratch/Gandi extension.\n一键增加成就&排行榜\n\nUse it for structured data, object/list serialization, and parsing workflows; AI service calls, prompts, generated content, or model-driven project features.\n\n## Core Concepts\n\n- Extension ID: `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard`.\n- DSL namespace: `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard`. Full opcodes use the form `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard_<opcode>`.\n- Use `getAllExtensions` or `getExtensionBlocks` when you need the live block list from the current project.\n- Use `getBlocksHelp` for any opcode before writing unfamiliar DSL, especially when menus or reporter inputs are involved.\n- Patch `/<target>/scripts/*.js` feature files. A file may contain multiple `// @script <id>` sections; each section must have exactly one top-level hat or stack.\n- Menu inputs should use the menu values listed in this guide or the live values returned by `getBlocksHelp`.\n\n## Recommended Flow\n\n1. Add the extension to the project if it is not already loaded.\n2. Read this guide with `getScratchGuide({ topic: \"extension-GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard\" })`.\n3. Use `getExtensionBlocks` or `getBlocksHelp` for the exact opcode and argument names you will patch.\n4. Write DSL with the namespace and opcode names below.\n5. Run `getDiagnostics` after patching scripts that use this extension.\n\nExample DSL shape:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.showAchievementList({ PAUSE: 0 });\nconst value = GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.hasAchievement({ ACHIEVE_ID: \"\" });\n```\n\n## Common Menu Values\n\n- `ACHIEVE_MENU` (also accepts reporters): dynamic menu.\n- `TOAST_MENU`: `GandiAchievement.toast`, `GandiAchievement.notToast`.\n- `PAUSE_MENU`: `GandiAchievement.pause`, `GandiAchievement.notPause`.\n- `UI_TYPE_MENU`: `GandiAchievement.type.leaderboard`, `GandiAchievement.type.achievement`.\n- `USER_DATA_TYPE_MENU`: `GandiAchievement.type.userId`, `GandiAchievement.type.username`, `GandiAchievement.type.score`.\n- `BOARD_DATA_TYPE_MENU`: `GandiAchievement.type.score`, `GandiAchievement.type.ranking`.\n\n## Blocks\n\n### Blocks\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.whenUIClose`\n\nBlock: `when [UI_TYPE] close`\n\nType: event hat.\n\nArguments:\n- `UI_TYPE`: text, menu `UI_TYPE_MENU`, default `leaderboard`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.whenUIClose({ UI_TYPE: \"leaderboard\" }, () => {\n  // extension actions here\n});\n```\n\n### GandiAchievement.reloadList\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.showAchievementList`\n\nBlock: `Open Achievement List and [PAUSE]`\n\nType: command.\n\nArguments:\n- `PAUSE`: number, menu `PAUSE_MENU`, default `0`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.showAchievementList({ PAUSE: 0 });\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.obtainAchievement`\n\nBlock: `obtain achievement [ACHIEVE_ID]`\n\nType: command.\n\nArguments:\n- `ACHIEVE_ID`: text, menu `ACHIEVE_MENU`, default ``.\n- `TOAST`: text, menu `TOAST_MENU`, default ``.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.obtainAchievement({ ACHIEVE_ID: \"\", TOAST: \"\" });\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.hasAchievement`\n\nBlock: `has achievement [ACHIEVE_ID]?`\n\nType: Boolean reporter.\n\nArguments:\n- `ACHIEVE_ID`: text, menu `ACHIEVE_MENU`, default ``.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.hasAchievement({ ACHIEVE_ID: \"\" })\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.hasAchievementByTemplateId`\n\nBlock: `has achievement[ACHIEVE_ID]?`\n\nType: Boolean reporter.\n\nArguments:\n- `ACHIEVE_ID`: text, default `id`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.hasAchievementByTemplateId({ ACHIEVE_ID: \"id\" })\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.updateAchievementExtra`\n\nBlock: `update achievement [ACHIEVE_ID] with extra [EXT]?`\n\nType: command.\n\nArguments:\n- `ACHIEVE_ID`: text, menu `ACHIEVE_MENU`, default ``.\n- `EXT`: text, default `love from scratcher`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.updateAchievementExtra({ ACHIEVE_ID: \"\", EXT: \"love from scratcher\" });\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.showLeaderboard`\n\nBlock: `show leaderboard[BOARD_ID]and[PAUSE]`\n\nType: command.\n\nArguments:\n- `BOARD_ID`: text, menu `BOARD_MENU`, default ``.\n- `PAUSE`: text, menu `PAUSE_MENU`, default `0`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.showLeaderboard({ BOARD_ID: \"\", PAUSE: \"0\" });\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.addUserScoreToLeaderboard`\n\nBlock: `add score[SCORE]to[BOARD_ID]with[LOG]`\n\nType: command.\n\nArguments:\n- `BOARD_ID`: text, menu `BOARD_MENU`, default ``.\n- `SCORE`: number, default `0`.\n- `LOG`: text, default `GandiAchievement.type.log`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.addUserScoreToLeaderboard({ BOARD_ID: \"\", SCORE: 0, LOG: \"GandiAchievement.type.log\" });\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.getUserDataFromLeaderboard`\n\nBlock: `user's[USER_DATA]in[BOARD_ID]at ranking[RANKING]`\n\nType: reporter.\n\nArguments:\n- `USER_DATA`: text, menu `USER_DATA_TYPE_MENU`, default `userId`.\n- `BOARD_ID`: text, menu `BOARD_MENU`, default ``.\n- `RANKING`: number, default `1`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.getUserDataFromLeaderboard({ USER_DATA: \"userId\", BOARD_ID: \"\", RANKING: 1 })\n```\n\n#### `GandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.getUserBoardDataFromLeaderboardByUserId`\n\nBlock: `user's [BOARD_DATA] in[BOARD_ID]`\n\nType: reporter.\n\nArguments:\n- `BOARD_ID`: text, menu `BOARD_MENU`, default ``.\n- `BOARD_DATA`: text, menu `BOARD_DATA_TYPE_MENU`, default `ranking`.\n\nDSL:\n\n```js\nGandiAchievementAndLeaderboard.getUserBoardDataFromLeaderboardByUserId({ BOARD_ID: \"\", BOARD_DATA: \"ranking\" })\n```\n\n## Pitfalls\n\n- Do not guess argument names from the visible block text; use the argument names shown above or from `getBlocksHelp`.\n- Menus may be localized in the UI. DSL usually needs the underlying menu value, not necessarily the translated label.\n- Reporter blocks can be nested inside other extension/core inputs; command blocks must be placed in a stack.\n- If a block has no static metadata here, inspect the current runtime because some extensions build blocks dynamically.\n- After changing scripts, run diagnostics and fix any unexpected input or menu errors before continuing.\n\n## Source\n\n- Extension source: `gandi_ccw_achievement/index.js`.\n- Generated from `D:/projects/scratch-extensions/src/extensions`.\n"
